               <p>
                  <table rows="3" cols="11">
                     <head>[<hi rend="italic">Remarks</hi>]<ref target="n070930-102" n="2"/>
                     </head>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">September</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">19th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">the leaves of some of the cottonwood begin to fade.    yes-<lb/>
terday saw the first Brant passing from the N. W. to<lb/>
S. E.—</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">20th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">the antelope is now ruting, the swallow<ref target="n070930-103" n="3"/> has disappeared<lb/>
12 days</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">21st</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">Antilopes ruting, as are the <hi rend="italic">Elk</hi>, the Buffaloe is nearly<lb/>
ceased—    the latter commence the latter end of July or<lb/>
first of August.</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">22nd</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">a little foggy this morning, a great number of green<lb/>
leged plove<ref target="n070930-104" n="4"/> passing down the river, also some geese &amp;<lb/>
brant—</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">23rd</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">aire remarkably dry-plumbs &amp; grapes fully ripe—    in<lb/>
36 hours two Spoonfuls of water aveporated in a sauser</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">24th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">three <name type="native_nation" key="Sioux Indians, Teton">tetons</name> swam the river and came to our encamp-<lb/>
ment this evening informed us that 30 longed [lodges]<lb/>
of their nation were near[by?]</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">[25]</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">This day the <name type="native_nation" key="Sioux Indians, Teton">Tetons</name> and ourselves had nearly come to<lb/>
an open a ruptr [rupture]</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">27th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">Saw a large flock of white Gulls with wings tiped with<lb/>
black<ref target="n070930-105" n="5"/>
                        </cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">28th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">this day about 12 oCk. had a severe struggle to get away<lb/>
from the <name type="native_nation" key="Sioux Indians, Teton">tetons</name>
                           <ref target="n070930-106" n="6"/>
                        </cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">29th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">〈the <name type="native_nation" key="Sioux Indians, Teton">Tetons</name>〉 the 2nd Chief came on Lard. Shore<ref target="n070930-107" n="7"/> we<lb/>
gave some tobacco and passed them over the river—<lb/>
saw Indns.</cell>
                     </row>
                     <row role="data">
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1"> </cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">30th</cell>
                        <cell role="data" rows="1" cols="1">passed the remainder of the band.<ref target="n070930-108" n="8"/>    gave tobacco, the<lb/>
chief left us<ref target="n070930-109" n="9"/>
                        </cell>
                     </row>
